Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.


[4.1] - 2022-08-30
Changed
- Small refactoring and optimization
- CHANGELOG updated
- Docstrings updated
- Updated requirements.txt


[4.0] - 2022-08-30
Added
- Two new optional parameters: --to_html and --to_pdf
- Save news to PDF option
- The font to save UTF-8 characters in the PDF

Changed
- Small refactoring
- Updated Manifest.in


[3.3] - 2022-08-27
Changed
- Readme doc updated
- CHANGELOG updated
- setup.py updated
- Refactoring and optimization


[3.2] - 2022-08-26
Changed
- RSS source URL is now converted to an optional argument
- Added and modified unit tests
- Updated requirements.txt and Manifest.in
- Refactoring and optimization


[3.1] - 2022-08-24
Added
- Added docstring

Changed
- Improvement in file processing
- Small refactoring


[3.0] - 2022-08-23
Added
- Implemented draft of work with files: creating, check if exist, reading, searching inside
- Added logging


[2.0] - 2022-08-22
Added
- Added setup.py

Changed
- Changed project structure
- Readme doc updated
- CHANGELOG updated
